{"TopicId":220380,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"Formula 1 KSC Driving Challenge","CreatedByName":"RevanX_LSR","CreatedById":216972,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-28T03:54:50Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"RevanX_LSR","CreatedById":216972,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-28T03:54:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022A159ZOd87MsQ.png?o=1\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002264.41\u0022 height=\u0022552\u0022 width=\u0022857\u0022 src=\u0022https://gcdnb.pbrd.co/images/A159ZOd87MsQ.png?o=1\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGoal: drive a car around the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E circuit as shown.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYour craft must be of the following design:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1 MK1 command pod\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n4 Small landing gear\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1 FL-T800 fuel tank\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1 Reliant Engine\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n4 2x2 structural plate.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSample run:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/IIEdUJ32uvs?feature=oembed\u0022 title=\u0022KSP F1 Circuit Sample Lap\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nby my old yt account of course\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRules:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStandard mode:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou must pass in between the buildings I did in the video shown above.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHardcore mode:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou must not pass on the grass and drive on the concrete, and you have to go up the crawlerway and onto the launch pad (